          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Extra option -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>At the title screen, press Up, Down, Left, Right, X, Circle. Then a new "Extra" option will appear that allows the game to be played with new enemies and alternate enemy positions.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Hidden Area 6 -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Select a character in versus mode. Then, highlight the random option on the area selection screen, hold L1, and press Circle.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Hidden Area 7 -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Select a character in versus mode. Then, highlight the random option on the area selection screen, hold L2, and press Circle.</font>&nbsp;<br>
